title: Number of hospitals in Finland 2007 to 2017
summary: Overall Number of hospitals has decreased over the Year.
Number of hospitals is slightly decreasing from 2011 to 2012, roughly constant from 2012 to 2014, slightly increasing from 2014 to 2015, and finally slightly decreasing from 2015 to 2016.
The most drastic decrease took place within the Year 2011 and 2012.
The highest Number of hospitals, of value 275.0 was reached at Year 2011
Minimum Number of hospitals about 258.0 was reached at Year 2014
